headline: Spotting Winners: United Therapeutics (NASDAQ:UTHR) And Therapeutics Stocks In Q4
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q4. Today, we are looking at therapeutics stocks, starting with United Therapeutics (NASDAQ:UTHR).
